description: (edit: A lot of confusion on what I meant in the video, I'm talking about wanting to see more khmer representation in the BEAUTY COMMUNITY here on youtube. Of course, I‚Äôll start speaking when I feel comfortable and when I practice more)  Thank you. All I can really say is thank you. You have all been so supportive of me ever since I started filming videos and I never knew that a hobby of mine could even impact a single person. I know I have a lot of bad days just like most of you, but I used to always live by the quote "what doesn't kill you makes you stronger" because we all endure hardships and battles that test our limits, but also is the driving force to help us grow.
